SEAM: Synthetic Estimated Average Matchup

The SEAM (synthetic estimated average matchup) application allows users to visualize synthetic spray chart distributions (batted-ball distributions) for any MLB batter-pitcher matchup that has occurred or could have occurred1 in the last four years.
